Allen and Steinfeld got married in June 2025, and announced they were expecting their first child together in December 2025.

Last week was eventful for the couple, as Allen led the Bills to a Wild Card win over the [Jacksonville Jaguars](https://www.foxnews.com/category/sports/nfl/jacksonville-jaguars) while Steinfeld presented an award at the Golden Globes. Steinfeld starred in 'Sinners,' which was up for seven awards, and won Best Original Score — Motion Picture and Cinematic and Box Office Achievement.

