It was the first road playoff win of Allen’s career. If the four-time Pro Bowler hopes to make it to his first career Super Bowl, he will have to take down [the Broncos](https://www.foxnews.com/category/sports/nfl/denver-broncos) on the road next.

The No. 6-seeded Bills take on the top-seeded Broncos at 4:30 p.m. ET on Saturday.

